2017 Zero FX
Electric Motorcycle



MSRP starting at: $8,495.00
Does not include government incentives.Does not include local shipping, applicable taxes,PDI, or road registration fees.










Model



FX ZF3.3 Modular



FX ZF6.5 (+$2,000.00) 



FX ZF6.5 Modular (+$2,500.00) 




Options




Quick-charge (+$600.00) 














Zero Motorcycles sells exclusively through authorized dealers. For purchase information, please select “Request a Quote” above or contact a Zero Motorcycles dealer.



The Zero FX comes ready to ride with a Z-Force® lithium ion power pack and on-board charger. MSRP does not include local shipping, applicable taxes, PDI and road registration fees. For information about pricing please contact your local dealer. You can also contact Zero Motorcycles directly and a representative will be happy to help answer any additional questions you may have.


To see if there is a dealer near you or to request a quote click here. If you don’t see a dealer in your area and are interested in purchasing a Zero then please contact us and we will do our best to have you riding a Zero soon.


Financing
Financing may be available through your local dealer. Zero Motorcycles also offers financing solutions to qualified customers in the event that there is no dealer in your area. For more information click here.


To schedule a demo ride, click here.
For news & info on upcoming products and to sign up for our newsletter, click here.
For general warranty information, click here.


Specifications are subject to change without notice. Imagery may not reflect most current product specifications. Zero Motorcycles reserves the right to make improvements and/or design changes without any obligation to previously sold, assembled or fabricated equipment.


* Does not include government incentives. Does not include local shipping, applicable taxes, PDI, or road registration fees.
















