2017 ZERO s

Overview
Zero SR
Features
Specs
Photos & videos
Pricing
Demo














Massive torque. More power.Greater acceleration.


Massive torque. Stunning acceleration. Instantaneous response. The Zero SR amps-up performance with a higher output (775 amp) controller and high temperature motor magnets. The result is a stunning 116 ft-lb of torque, more than any 1,000cc sport bike. With arm-stretching acceleration and higher sustained top speeds, the Zero SR leaves gas-powered competition in the dust.


See Features
